right-click-file (1.0.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Nautilus extension: right-click menu in all folders.
  * DING patch: right-click menu on the GNOME desktop.
  * GLib.spawn_async() used for path safety.
  * Installation log written to /var/log/right_click_file/.

